Access off main road to the car park then under up and down lines. Walk along the up cess to a point opposite the signal box entrance and across up and down running lines to box.
Access over footbridge, then along York road and through the gate to the relay room entrance.
Leave via main exit. up side. and procede through arcade of shops. Just before supermarket there is a gate on the left at rear of p way hut leading to the relay room.
Access from station through fence, towards sidings, then walk around the warehouse complex and cross the line to the relay cabin.
